            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">• <span style="color:#888;">Spring 2026:</span> SNT purchases condo for <span style="color: #66ccff;">${{formatNumber (or scenario.total_mortgage_amount 350000)}}</span> w/ closing costs, placing <span style="color: #66ccff;">${{formatNumber (multiply (or scenario.total_mortgage_amount 350000) (or scenario.mortgage_split_pct 0.80))}}</span> down (<span style="color: #66ccff;">{{multiply (or scenario.mortgage_split_pct 0.80) 100}}%</span>), remaining <span style="color: #66ccff;">${{formatNumber (multiply (or scenario.total_mortgage_amount 350000) (subtract 1 (or scenario.mortgage_split_pct 0.80)))}}</span> condo mortgage (<span style="color: #66ccff;">{{subtract 100 (multiply (or scenario.mortgage_split_pct 0.80) 100)}}%</span> 30yr P&I). No primary house refinance.</li>
